high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the sink, then turn right and walk up to the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap that is in the tub.
Put the bar of soap in the sink basin and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean bar of soap.
Turn around and walk over to the toilet.
Put the clean bar of soap on top of the toilet tank standing up.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Take a step to the left and face the bath tub.
Pick up the bar of soap from the left side of the bath tub.
Carry the soap and turn to the left and find the sink.
Place the soap inside the sink. Turn on the water and and off again. Pick up the soap.
Carry the soap and turn around. Move to the toilet and turn to the left to face it.
Place the soap on the tank of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Rinse of a bar of soap and place it on the toilet tank.

high_descs: Take a step left and ahead to the tub.
Pick up the bar of soap.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Rinse the soap in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the right side of the toilet.
Place the soap on the toilet tank behind the candle.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a toilet tank.
